OL,3,CNHS 'failed one of their own' after
OL,4,Cretired worker takes own life
OL,6,F"Looking after his family was his
OL,7,Fnumber one priority," she said. "Tony
OL,8,Fwould never have even considered
OL,9,Ftaking his own life when he was a fit
OL,10,Fand well man."
OL,12,FSimon added: "He had no life. From
OL,13,FSeptember 2023 it just nose-dived out
OL,14,Fof control, that was the first time he
OL,15,Fcontemplated taking his own life.
OL,17,F"Thankfully he went to A&E. I just
OL,18,Fgrabbed hold of him and said please
OL,19,Fdon't do it again.
