OL,3,CNHS 'failed one of their own' after
OL,4,Cretired worker takes own life
OL,6,F"He'd had enough, he'd had enough of
OL,7,Fthe pain."
OL,9,FIn December 2023, Tony disappeared
OL,10,Ffrom his home in Trafford, Manchester,
OL,11,Fsparking a three-month search.
OL,13,FHis body was found in the River Mersey
OL,14,Fin March 2024, it was his sixth
OL,15,Fattempt to take his own life.
OL,17,FAn inquest into his death highlighted
OL,18,Fthe challenges of managing complex
OL,19,Fcases like Tony's.
