OL,3,CNHS 'failed one of their own' after
OL,4,Cretired worker takes own life
OL,6,FAssistant Coroner Adrian Farrow said:
OL,7,F"The absence of a collaborative and
OL,8,Fcoordinated approach contributed to a
OL,9,Ffeeling of hopelessness."
OL,11,FHe has issued a Report to Prevent
OL,12,FFuture Deaths, urging the Department
OL,13,Fof Health and Social Care (DHSC) to
OL,14,Faddress communication gaps within the
OL,15,FNHS.
OL,17,FWhile the coroner could not confirm
OL,18,Fwhether improved care would have
OL,19,Fprevented Tony's death, he noted that
OL,20,Fbetter coordination might have
OL,21,Falleviated his distress.
