OL,3,CNHS 'failed one of their own' after
OL,4,Cretired worker takes own life
OL,6,FThe DHSC has pledged to review the
OL,7,Ffindings stating: "It is unacceptable
OL,8,Fthat patients are not receiving joined-
OL,9,Fup care when they need it."
OL,11,F"Our deepest sympathies go out to Mr
OL,12,FWilliamson's family in this tragic
OL,13,Fcase. We consider every Prevention of
OL,14,FFuture Deaths report carefully and
OL,15,Fwill respond in due course," a DHSC
OL,16,FSpokesperson added.
OL,18,F"This government's 10 Year Health Plan
OL,19,Fwill fix the broken system to make the
OL,20,FNHS fit for the future.
